<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" xmlns:slash="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/" xmlns:sy="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/" xmlns:wfw="http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/"><channel><title>生活黑客</title><link/>https://lifehacker.com/feed/rss<description>凡事都做得更好。</description><pubDate> Tue, 17 Dec 2024 17:51:11 +0000</pubDate><language> en-us </language><atom:link href="https://lifehacker.com/feed/rss" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"></atom:link><lastbuilddate> 2024 年 12 月 17 日星期二 17:51:11 +0000</lastbuilddate><copyright>版权所有 2024 Ziff Davis, LLC。版权所有。</copyright><ttl> 15</ttl><sy:updateperiod>每小时</sy:updateperiod><sy:updatefrequency>1</sy:updatefrequency><item><title>让您的房客更舒适（并减轻您自己的压力）的五种方法</title><guid ispermalink="false">01JF8QV6N7HNBC6AH5QBKSNN9V</guid><pubDate> Tue, 17 Dec 2024 17:30:56 +0000</pubDate><description>当客人开始走进大门时，现在做一些准备就会得到回报。 </description><media:thumbnail url="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01JF8QV6N7HNBC6AH5QBKSNN9V/hero-image.png"></media:thumbnail><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>我们可以通过此页面上的链接赚取佣金。</p><p>假期接待是一项艰苦的工作，即使尽最大努力让您的客人尽可能舒适，<a href="https://lifehacker.com/home/how-to-prepare-home-for-guests" target="_blank">体验也可能会充满压力</a>。减少压力并最大化客人体验的一个有用的心态是提供您喜欢的设施（或希望提供度假租赁），这也将使您的客人在住宿期间感到舒适和自给自足。</p><h2 id="provide-options-for-temperature-control">提供温度控制选项</h2><p>您可能不希望具有不同室内温度偏好的客人调整您的恒温器，或者因为您家中太热或太冷而默默忍受，尤其是在晚上。提前在卧室配备风扇和/或小型取暖器以及额外的毯子，以便客人在睡眠时感到舒适。当你这样做的时候，请确保你有足够的枕头可供使用，不要让每个人的供应都太薄。 </p><div class="pogoClear mb-12 mt-10 rounded-md border-2 border-gray-100 py-7 shadow-xl md:py-6"><div class="order-1 mx-auto flex flex-col justify-center md:order-2 md:ml-4 md:w-full md:grow"><div class="block cursor-pointer text-center font-akshar text-2xl font-medium leading-7 text-brand-green duration-200 ease-in-out hover:text-brand-green-700 md:text-left md:text-xl md:leading-6"> Jollyvogue 睡眠枕头</div><div class="mt-4 hidden md:flex md:justify-between"><div class="self-end"><div class="mb-0 h-11 md:flex md:flex-col md:justify-center"><div class=" font-sans leading-4 text-black"><div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-1 md:justify-start"><span class="font-bold"><span class="font-medium">亚马逊</span>20.99 美元</span><img class="mt-0 h-[15px]" src="/images/amazon-prime.svg" title="亚马逊 Prime" alt="Amazon Prime"></div><div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-x-1 font-bold md:justify-start"> <span class="text-sm line-through">$39.99</span><span class="text-sm text-brand-green">节省 $19.00</span></div></div></div></div><div class="w-44 self-end"> <button class="flex justify-center items-center w-full bg-brand-green text-white text-base font-sans font-medium rounded-md hover:bg-brand-green-700 hover:cursor-pointer md:text-sm h-11">立即购买</button></div></div></div><div class="order-2 mt-5 h-auto w-full md:order-1 md:mt-0 md:hidden"><div class="flex aspect-video items-center justify-center"><img class="m-0 max-h-full max-w-full rounded-md" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/product/04v5pOxuu0LNh31SJUODigj/hero-image.fill.size_autoxauto.v1707306596.jpg" alt="Jollyvogue 睡眠枕头" width="auto" height="auto" loading="lazy"></div></div><div class="order-2 ml-2 hidden w-32 shrink-0 items-center md:order-1 md:ml-0 md:flex"><div class="flex aspect-video items-center justify-center"><img class="m-0 max-h-full max-w-full rounded-md" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/product/04v5pOxuu0LNh31SJUODigj/hero-image.fill.size_autoxauto.v1707306596.jpg" alt="Jollyvogue 睡眠枕头" width="auto" height="auto" loading="lazy"></div></div><div class="order-3 flex grow flex-wrap md:hidden md:grow-0"><div class="mt-4 w-full"> <button class="flex justify-center items-center w-full bg-brand-green text-white text-base font-sans font-medium rounded-md hover:bg-brand-green-700 hover:cursor-pointer md:text-sm h-11">立即购买</button></div><div class="mx-2 mt-4 w-full"><div class=" font-sans leading-4 text-black"><div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-1 md:justify-start"><span class="font-bold"><span class="font-medium">亚马逊</span>20.99 美元</span><img class="mt-0 h-[15px]" src="/images/amazon-prime.svg" title="亚马逊 Prime" alt="Amazon Prime"></div><div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-x-1 font-bold md:justify-start"> <span class="text-sm line-through">$39.99</span><span class="text-sm text-brand-green">节省 $19.00</span></div></div></div></div></div></div><h2 id="stock-bathrooms-like-a-fancy-hotel">浴室就像豪华酒店一样</h2><p>虽然有些客人可能会携带所有可能使用的盥洗用品旅行，但其他客人会喜欢手头上有一些物品，就像他们在一家不错的酒店中可能会找到的那样：洗发水、护发素、肥皂/沐浴露、乳液和纸巾是显而易见的选择。但您还可以进一步添加牙膏、牙线、牙刷和基本急救用品（绷带、止痛药、润唇膏等）。其他额外设施，如吹风机、棉球、棉签、化妆巾和经期卫生用品也很贴心。</p><p>最后，提前在浴室里堆放足够的卫生纸和干净的毛巾，以防止客人稍后询问或借用这些物品，并确保客房的门后有额外的挂钩，以便每个人都有地方悬挂将湿毛巾擦干。</p><h2 id="place-extra-chargers-around-the-house">在房子周围放置额外的充电器</h2><p>同样，有些客人会配备所有设备的电源线和充电器，但在最需要的地方（例如床头柜下方和人流量大的公共区域）插入额外设备是一种很好的感觉。显然，您可能无法拥有所有类型的电缆，但 USB-C 是一个不错的选择——Lightning 和 Micro USB 也很不错。您还应该考虑清理插座中不需要的电线，为客用充电器腾出空间。 </p><div class="pogoClear mb-12 mt-10 rounded-md border-2 border-gray-100 py-7 shadow-xl md:py-6"><div class="order-1 mx-auto flex flex-col justify-center md:order-2 md:ml-4 md:w-full md:grow"><div class="block cursor-pointer text-center font-akshar text-2xl font-medium leading-7 text-brand-green duration-200 ease-in-out hover:text-brand-green-700 md:text-left md:text-xl md:leading-6"> 6 英尺 USB-C 充电器（2 件装） </div><div class="mt-4 hidden md:flex md:justify-between"><div class="self-end"><div class="mb-0 h-11 md:flex md:flex-col md:justify-center"><div class=" font-sans leading-4 text-black"><div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-1 md:justify-start"><span class="font-bold"><span class="font-medium">亚马逊</span>7.98 美元</span><img class="mt-0 h-[15px]" src="/images/amazon-prime.svg" title="亚马逊 Prime" alt="Amazon Prime"></div><div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-x-1 font-bold md:justify-start"> <span class="text-sm line-through">$9.98</span><span class="text-sm text-brand-green">节省 $2.00</span></div></div></div></div><div class="w-44 self-end"> <button class="flex justify-center items-center w-full bg-brand-green text-white text-base font-sans font-medium rounded-md hover:bg-brand-green-700 hover:cursor-pointer md:text-sm h-11">立即购买</button></div></div></div><div class="order-2 mt-5 h-auto w-full md:order-1 md:mt-0 md:hidden"><div class="flex aspect-video items-center justify-center"><img class="m-0 max-h-full max-w-full rounded-md" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/product/01LIbaUxCK0iAY5CzVFybF3/hero-image.fill.size_autoxauto.v1734446456.jpg" alt="C 型充电器，2 件装 25W C 型超级快速充电座，带 6 英尺 USB C 充电线，兼容 Galaxy S23 Ultra/S23+/S22/S21/S20" width="auto" height="auto" loading="lazy"></div></div><div class="order-2 ml-2 hidden w-32 shrink-0 items-center md:order-1 md:ml-0 md:flex"><div class="flex aspect-video items-center justify-center"><img class="m-0 max-h-full max-w-full rounded-md" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/product/01LIbaUxCK0iAY5CzVFybF3/hero-image.fill.size_autoxauto.v1734446456.jpg" alt="C 型充电器，2 件装 25W C 型超级快速充电座，带 6 英尺 USB C 充电线，兼容 Galaxy S23 Ultra/S23+/S22/S21/S20" width="auto" height="auto" loading="lazy"></div></div><div class="order-3 flex grow flex-wrap md:hidden md:grow-0"><div class="mt-4 w-full"> <button class="flex justify-center items-center w-full bg-brand-green text-white text-base font-sans font-medium rounded-md hover:bg-brand-green-700 hover:cursor-pointer md:text-sm h-11">立即购买</button></div><div class="mx-2 mt-4 w-full"><div class=" font-sans leading-4 text-black"><div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-1 md:justify-start"><span class="font-bold"><span class="font-medium">亚马逊</span>7.98 美元</span><img class="mt-0 h-[15px]" src="/images/amazon-prime.svg" title="亚马逊 Prime" alt="Amazon Prime"></div><div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-x-1 font-bold md:justify-start"> <span class="text-sm line-through">$9.98</span><span class="text-sm text-brand-green">节省 $2.00</span></div></div></div></div></div></div><h2 id="add-night-lights">添加夜灯</h2><p>您很可能可以像忍者一样在黑暗中穿过自己的房子；因此，除非您有小孩，否则您可能不会意识到对于不习惯晚上在走廊里行走的客人来说，几盏夜灯有多么重要。特别是在走廊和浴室添加夜灯，这样就不会有人在黑暗中摸索。您甚至可以在每间客房中放置一个，以便客人可以选择对他们最有帮助的位置。您可以在亚马逊上<a href="https://zdcs.link/QORqo8?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Explainers&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=as%20little%20as%20%245%20per%20light&amp;short_url=QORqo8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开">以每灯 5 美元的价格</a>购买插入式运动传感器灯包。 </p><div class="pogoClear mb-12 mt-10 rounded-md border-2 border-gray-100 py-7 shadow-xl md:py-6"><div class="order-1 mx-auto flex flex-col justify-center md:order-2 md:ml-4 md:w-full md:grow"><div class="block cursor-pointer text-center font-akshar text-2xl font-medium leading-7 text-brand-green duration-200 ease-in-out hover:text-brand-green-700 md:text-left md:text-xl md:leading-6"> L LOHAS LED 运动传感器夜灯，2 件装，运动激活夜灯，夜灯插入墙壁运动传感器，3000K 暖白色，可调亮度 30/60LM，适合儿童成人浴室卧室</div><div class="mt-4 hidden md:flex md:justify-between"><div class="self-end"><div class="mb-0 h-11 md:flex md:flex-col md:justify-center"><div class=" font-sans leading-4 text-black"><div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-1 md:justify-start"><span class="font-bold"><span class="font-medium">亚马逊</span>12.99 美元</span><img class="mt-0 h-[15px]" src="/images/amazon-prime.svg" title="亚马逊 Prime" alt="Amazon Prime"></div><div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-x-1 font-bold md:justify-start"> <span class="text-sm line-through">$15.99</span><span class="text-sm text-brand-green">节省 $3.00</span></div></div></div></div><div class="w-44 self-end"> <button class="flex justify-center items-center w-full bg-brand-green text-white text-base font-sans font-medium rounded-md hover:bg-brand-green-700 hover:cursor-pointer md:text-sm h-11">立即购买</button></div></div></div><div class="order-2 mt-5 h-auto w-full md:order-1 md:mt-0 md:hidden"><div class="flex aspect-video items-center justify-center"><img class="m-0 max-h-full max-w-full rounded-md" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/product/04bUCIXy1vCkp7VESdhgm3T/hero-image.fill.size_autoxauto.v1734387950.jpg" alt="L LOHAS LED 运动传感器夜灯，2 件装，运动激活夜灯，夜灯插入墙壁运动传感器，3000K 暖白色，可调亮度 30/60LM，适合儿童成人浴室卧室" width="auto" height="auto" loading="lazy"></div></div><div class="order-2 ml-2 hidden w-32 shrink-0 items-center md:order-1 md:ml-0 md:flex"><div class="flex aspect-video items-center justify-center"><img class="m-0 max-h-full max-w-full rounded-md" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/product/04bUCIXy1vCkp7VESdhgm3T/hero-image.fill.size_autoxauto.v1734387950.jpg" alt="L LOHAS LED 运动传感器夜灯，2 件装，运动激活夜灯，夜灯插入墙壁运动传感器，3000K 暖白色，可调亮度 30/60LM，适合儿童成人浴室卧室" width="auto" height="auto" loading="lazy"></div></div><div class="order-3 flex grow flex-wrap md:hidden md:grow-0"><div class="mt-4 w-full"> <button class="flex justify-center items-center w-full bg-brand-green text-white text-base font-sans font-medium rounded-md hover:bg-brand-green-700 hover:cursor-pointer md:text-sm h-11">立即购买</button></div><div class="mx-2 mt-4 w-full"><div class=" font-sans leading-4 text-black"><div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-1 md:justify-start"><span class="font-bold"><span class="font-medium">亚马逊</span>12.99 美元</span><img class="mt-0 h-[15px]" src="/images/amazon-prime.svg" title="亚马逊 Prime" alt="Amazon Prime"></div><div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-x-1 font-bold md:justify-start"> <span class="text-sm line-through">$15.99</span><span class="text-sm text-brand-green">节省 $3.00</span></div></div></div></div></div></div><h2 id="collect-snack-and-breakfast-requests-ahead-of-time">提前收集小吃和早餐请求</h2><p>为客人做准备的一个周到的方法是，当他们到达时，手头上准备一些他们喜欢的食物，这样他们就可以自由地吃零食，而不会因为搜查冰箱或食品储藏室而感到内疚。计划买一些麦片、燕麦片或他们喜欢吃的其他早餐主食，这样他们就可以在起床准备开始新的一天时享用快速而简单的早餐。</p> ]]>;</content:encoded><link/> https://lifehacker.com/home/how-to-make-houseguests-more-comfortable<dc:creator>艾米丽·朗</dc:creator><category><![CDATA[Home & Garden]]></category></item><item><title>我是一名跑步者，这些防水跑鞋改变了游戏规则</title><guid ispermalink="false">01JFAHR3RCYSC0DSWTSSMEZMK7</guid><pubDate> Tue, 17 Dec 2024 17:00:00 +0000</pubDate><description>即使在冬季跑步，双脚也温暖、干燥？这些是送给您生命中跑步者的完美礼物。 </description><media:thumbnail url="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01JFAHR3RCYSC0DSWTSSMEZMK7/hero-image.png"></media:thumbnail><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>我们可以通过此页面上的链接赚取佣金。</p><p>如果您认识跑步者，我会为您推荐完美的礼物。如果您<em>是</em>跑步者，我知道您应该告诉妈妈您想要什么圣诞节礼物。即使您近期没有送礼节日，您仍然应该知道有关防水跑鞋的好消息。它们就在那里，可能现在正在打折，它们将改变你的生活。 </p><div class="pogoClear mb-12 mt-10 rounded-md border-2 border-gray-100 py-7 shadow-xl md:py-6"><div class="order-1 mx-auto flex flex-col justify-center md:order-2 md:ml-4 md:w-full md:grow"><div class="block cursor-pointer text-center font-akshar text-2xl font-medium leading-7 text-brand-green duration-200 ease-in-out hover:text-brand-green-700 md:text-left md:text-xl md:leading-6"> Nike Pegasus Trail 4 Gore-TEX 女式防水越野跑鞋（FN7102-010，黑色/浅洋红色/粉色泡沫/叶绿素）9 号</div><div class="mt-4 hidden md:flex md:justify-between"><div class="self-end"><div class="mb-0 h-11 md:flex md:flex-col md:justify-center"><div class=" font-sans leading-4 text-black"><div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-1 md:justify-start"><span class="font-bold"><span class="font-medium">亚马逊</span>184.99 美元</span></div><div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-x-1 font-bold md:justify-start"><span class="text-sm line-through">$193.94</span><span class="text-sm text-brand-green">节省 $8.95</span></div></div></div></div><div class="w-44 self-end"> <button class="flex justify-center items-center w-full bg-brand-green text-white text-base font-sans font-medium rounded-md hover:bg-brand-green-700 hover:cursor-pointer md:text-sm h-11">立即购买</button></div></div></div><div class="order-2 mt-5 h-auto w-full md:order-1 md:mt-0 md:hidden"><div class="flex aspect-video items-center justify-center"><img class="m-0 max-h-full max-w-full rounded-md" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/product/06XGC3Ymt61DP5Ojjyg3FcU/hero-image.fill.size_autoxauto.v1734447322.jpg" alt="Nike Pegasus Trail 4 Gore-TEX 女式防水越野跑鞋（FN7102-010，黑色/浅洋红色/粉色泡沫/叶绿素）9 号" width="auto" height="auto" loading="lazy"></div></div><div class="order-2 ml-2 hidden w-32 shrink-0 items-center md:order-1 md:ml-0 md:flex"><div class="flex aspect-video items-center justify-center"><img class="m-0 max-h-full max-w-full rounded-md" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/product/06XGC3Ymt61DP5Ojjyg3FcU/hero-image.fill.size_autoxauto.v1734447322.jpg" alt="Nike Pegasus Trail 4 Gore-TEX 女式防水越野跑鞋（FN7102-010，黑色/浅洋红色/粉色泡沫/叶绿素）9 号" width="auto" height="auto" loading="lazy"></div></div><div class="order-3 flex grow flex-wrap md:hidden md:grow-0"><div class="mt-4 w-full"> <button class="flex justify-center items-center w-full bg-brand-green text-white text-base font-sans font-medium rounded-md hover:bg-brand-green-700 hover:cursor-pointer md:text-sm h-11">立即购买</button></div><div class="mx-2 mt-4 w-full"><div class=" font-sans leading-4 text-black"><div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-1 md:justify-start"><span class="font-bold"><span class="font-medium">亚马逊</span>184.99 美元</span></div><div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-x-1 font-bold md:justify-start"><span class="text-sm line-through">$193.94</span><span class="text-sm text-brand-green">节省 $8.95</span></div></div></div></div></div></div><p>我是根据经验说话的。不久前，我的生日快到了，我不知道该告诉妈妈我想要什么。 （她不断地问。） 当我<a href="https://lifehacker.com/best-ways-to-find-a-running-track-near-you" target="_blank"><u>在当地的跑道上</u></a>慢跑时，我在思考这个问题，在一场近乎冰冻的毛毛细雨中，我的脚趾每走一步都在<em>挤压</em>。我突然想起有Gore-Tex鞋的存在。我几年前拥有一双并且很喜欢它们，但当它们磨损时我从未更换过它们。不知怎的，他们感觉太奢侈了。大多数跑步者都会穿着普通的鞋子和羊毛袜来度过潮湿的天气，所以为什么不凑合呢？</p><p>我会告诉你为什么不。羊毛袜可以让双脚保暖，但不能保持双脚<em>干燥</em>。如果您去公园跑步，那么您开车回家时双脚都会湿透。你会回到家，拧干你的袜子，并且必须让你的鞋子通风，并希望在你下次跑步时它们已经基本干燥。穿上湿鞋和穿上湿泳衣一样有趣。相比之下，在毛毛细雨中跑步回家，双脚干燥，是这个残酷世界最伟大的物质享受之一。</p><h2 id="what-weather-are-water-resistant-shoes-good-for">防水鞋适合什么天气？</h2><p>防水鞋非常适合在毛毛雨或雪天穿着。穿普通鞋子时，你的体温往往会融化接触鞋子的雪，即使在冰点以下的日子也会让你的脚湿漉漉的。防水鞋非常适合下雪、地面上有少量积雪或下雨时穿着。这几乎涵盖了宾夕法尼亚州冬季我可能认为适合跑步的所有天气。</p><h2 id="what-dont-water-resistant-shoes-do">防水鞋没有什么作用？</h2><p>不过，防水并不<em>防水</em>。使用 Gore-Tex 和类似材料，您无法踏入齐踝深的水坑并期望保持干燥。一场足够大的倾盆大雨最终可能会穿过或绕过材料。</p><p>请注意，防水鞋材料并不能阻止雪或雨进入鞋顶。为了在深雪中跋涉，您可能需要安装护腿（或购买带有内置护腿的鞋子）。</p><p>如果您在各种寒冷的条件下跑步，您可能还希望鞋底有更多的抓地力。您可以购买内置鞋钉的鞋子，或者<a href="https://zdcs.link/a0nB0p?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Opinions&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=add%20your%20own&amp;short_url=a0nB0p&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开"><u>添加您自己的鞋钉</u></a>。</p><h2 id="what-are-the-best-water-resistant-running-shoes">最好的防水跑鞋是什么？</h2><p>我知道您很想看到我的鞋，所以它们就是： <a href="https://zdcs.link/9Z5nKR?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Opinions&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=Nike%20InfinityRN%20Gore-Tex&amp;short_url=9Z5nKR&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开"><u>Nike InfinityRN Gore-Tex</u></a> 。 （我的是白色的。）说实话，我没有做很多研究，也不会发誓这些是最好的。我的要求是（1）防水，（2）耐克，因为耐克总是很适合我。这些符合要求，我在雨雪中穿着它们进行了许多愉快的跑步。 </p><div class="pogoClear mb-12 mt-10 rounded-md border-2 border-gray-100 py-7 shadow-xl md:py-6"><div class="order-1 mx-auto flex flex-col justify-center md:order-2 md:ml-4 md:w-full md:grow"><div class="block cursor-pointer text-center font-akshar text-2xl font-medium leading-7 text-brand-green duration-200 ease-in-out hover:text-brand-green-700 md:text-left md:text-xl md:leading-6"> Nike InfinityRN 4 Gore-Tex 女式防水跑鞋</div><div class="mt-4 hidden md:flex md:justify-between"><div class="self-end"><div class="mb-0 h-11 md:flex md:flex-col md:justify-center"><div class=" font-sans leading-4 text-black"><div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-1 md:just